The following packages may be supported by the UMTS Bearer Independent Circuit-Switched Core Network as required by the network services deployed in the network:
-	Circuit Switched Data package (see clause 15.2.1);
-	TFO package (see clause 15.2.2);
-	3G Expanded Call Progress Tones Generator package (see clause 15.2.3);
-	Modification of Link Characteristics Bearer Capabiltity package (see clause 15.2.4);
-	Enhanced Circuit Switched Data package (see clause 15.2.5);
-	Cellular Text telephone Modem Text Transport package (see clause 15.2.6);
-	IP transport package (see clause 15.2.7);
-	Flexible Tone Generator Package (see clause 15.2.8);
-	Trace Package (see clause 15.2.9);
-	ASCI Group Call package (see clause 15.2.10);
-	3G Interface Type package.
